    Supabase -->|"requests generated\nspecies icons / art"| ImageGen
    Railway -->|"serves static\nweb build"| Player
    PgCron -->|"triggers scheduled\nenrichment jobs"| Supabase

    style EarthNova fill:#4a9eff,color:#fff
    style Player fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
